enum PokeColor {
    grass = '#2dcd45',
    poison = '#883688',
    fire = '#f08030',
    flying = '#a890f0',
    water = '#149eff',
    bug = '#a8b820',
    normal = '#a8a878',
    electric = '#f8d030',
    ground = '#e0c068',
    fairy = '#ee99ac',
    fighting = '#94352d',
    psychic = '#ff6996',
    rock = '#b8a038',
    steel = '#b8b8d0',
    ice = '#98d8d8',
    ghost = '#614c83',
    dragon = '#700aee'
}

export default PokeColor;
